在[[醫學|醫學]]上，'''關節注射'''（{{lang-en|Joint injection}}）或'''關節內注射'''（{{lang-en|Intra-articular injection}}）是用來治療[[關節|關節]]部位[[發炎|發炎]]性疾病的一種處置，比如[[類風濕性關節炎|類風濕性關節炎]]、[[乾癬性關節炎|乾癬性關節炎]]、[[痛風|痛風]]、[[肌腱炎|肌腱炎]]、[[滑囊炎|滑囊炎]]、[[腕隧道症候群|腕隧道症候群]]<ref name="CarpalTunnelReview.com">{{cite web|url=http://www.carpaltunnelreview.com|title=Carpal Tunnel Review|date=25 July 2013|publisher=JohnDRhoads|accessdate=25 July 2013|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130730124449/http://carpaltunnelreview.com/|archivedate=30 July 2013}}</ref>，偶爾用於[[骨關節炎|骨關節炎]]<ref name="freedict">{{cite web |url=http://medical-dictionary.thefreedictionary.com/intraarticular+injection |title=intraarticular injection - definition |year=2010 |work=TheFreeDictionary.com |publisher=Farlex |accessdate=9 June 2010 |archive-date=2017-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202073657/http://medical-dictionary.thefreedictionary.com/intraarticular+injection |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Wen2000">{{cite web|url=http://www.aafp.org/afp/20000801/565.html|title=Intra-articular Hyaluronic Acid Injections for Knee Osteoarthritis|last=Wen|first=Dennis Y|date=1 August 2000|publisher=American Academy of Family Physicians|accessdate=9 June 2010|archive-date=2011-06-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110624000820/http://www.aafp.org/afp/20000801/565.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。將皮下注射針頭插入患部關節，注入一次劑量的一種[[抗炎性|抗炎性]][[藥物|藥物]]，最常見的是[[皮質類固醇|皮質類固醇]]。[[玻尿酸|玻尿酸]]由於其高[[黏度|黏度]]，有時可用來取代[[滑囊|滑囊]]液，注入關節作為補充<ref name="Wen2000" />。這個技術也可用於從關節中抽走過多的關節液<ref name="freedict" />。

== 用於骨關節炎的療效 ==
用於[[骨關節炎|骨關節炎]]的病患，關節注射[[糖皮質素|糖皮質素]]（例如[[氫羥腎上腺皮質素|氫羥腎上腺皮質素]]）可短期舒緩疼痛，持續時間約幾周到幾個月之間<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Arroll B, Goodyear-Smith F | title = Corticosteroid injections for osteoarthritis of the knee: meta-analysis | journal = BMJ | volume = 328 | issue = 7444 | pages = 869 | date = April 2004 | pmid = 15039276 | pmc = 387479 | doi = 10.1136/bmj.38039.573970.7C }}</ref>。與[[安慰劑|安慰劑]]相比，玻尿酸注射液對[[膝|膝]]關節炎沒有助益<ref name=Rutjes12>{{cite journal | vauthors = Rutjes AW, Jüni P, da Costa BR, Trelle S, Nüesch E, Reichenbach S | title = Viscosupplementation for osteoarthritis of the knee: a systematic review and meta-analysis | journal = Annals of Internal Medicine | volume = 157 | issue = 3 | pages = 180–91 | date = August 2012 | pmid = 22868835 | doi = 10.7326/0003-4819-157-3-201208070-00473 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Jevsevar D, Donnelly P, Brown GA, Cummins DS | title = Viscosupplementation for Osteoarthritis of the Knee: A Systematic Review of the Evidence | journal = The Journal of Bone and Joint Surgery. American Volume | volume = 97 | issue = 24 | pages = 2047–60 | date = December 2015 | pmid = 26677239 | doi = 10.2106/jbjs.n.00743 }}</ref>，但會增加後續疼痛的風險<ref name=Rutjes12/>。用於[[踝|踝]]骨關節炎，相關證據尚不充足<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Witteveen AG, Hofstad CJ, Kerkhoffs GM | title = Hyaluronic acid and other conservative treatment options for osteoarthritis of the ankle | journal = The Cochrane Database of Systematic Reviews | volume = 10 | issue = 10 | pages = CD010643 | date = October 2015 | pmid = 26475434 | doi = 10.1002/14651858.CD010643.pub2 | quote = It is unclear if there is a benefit or harm for HA as treatment for ankle OA }}</ref>。[[高濃度血小板血漿|高濃度血小板血漿]]的注射效果尚不明朗，有些研究認為可以改善功能，但不能改善疼痛，並且會增加風險<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Khoshbin A, Leroux T, Wasserstein D, Marks P, Theodoropoulos J, Ogilvie-Harris D, Gandhi R, Takhar K, Lum G, Chahal J | title = The efficacy of platelet-rich plasma in the treatment of symptomatic knee osteoarthritis: a systematic review with quantitative synthesis | journal = Arthroscopy | volume = 29 | issue = 12 | pages = 2037–48 | date = December 2013 | pmid = 24286802 | doi = 10.1016/j.arthro.2013.09.006 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Rodriguez-Merchan EC | title = Intraarticular Injections of Platelet-rich Plasma (PRP) in the Management of Knee Osteoarthritis | journal = The Archives of Bone and Joint Surgery | volume = 1 | issue = 1 | pages = 5–8 | date = September 2013 | pmid = 25207275 | pmc = 4151401 }}</ref>。

2015年的[[考科藍|考科藍]]文獻回顧發現膝關節內注射皮質類固醇不能改善[[生活品質|生活品質]]，並且對膝[[關節|關節]]間隙沒有幫助，由於其研究品質較差，無法確定其注射後1至6週的臨床效果<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Jüni P, Hari R, Rutjes AW, Fischer R, Silletta MG, Reichenbach S, da Costa BR | title = Intra-articular corticosteroid for knee osteoarthritis | journal = The Cochrane Database of Systematic Reviews | issue = 10 | pages = CD005328 | date = October 2015 | pmid = 26490760 | doi = 10.1002/14651858.CD005328.pub3 | df =  | url = http://boris.unibe.ch/73451/1/J%C3%BCni%20CochraneSystRev%202015.pdf | access-date = 2020-01-24 | archive-date = 2021-03-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210321172526/https://boris.unibe.ch/73451/1/J%C3%BCni%20CochraneSystRev%202015.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>。2015年的另一項研究報導了高劑量關節內注射皮質類固醇的不良反應<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Wernecke C, Braun HJ, Dragoo JL | title = The Effect of Intra-articular Corticosteroids on Articular Cartilage: A Systematic Review | journal = Orthopaedic Journal of Sports Medicine | volume = 3 | issue = 5 | pages = 2325967115581163 | date = May 2015 | pmid = 26674652 | pmc = 4622344 | doi = 10.1177/2325967115581163 }}</ref>，2017年的一項試驗，每12周注射[[去炎松|去炎松]]持續2年，與安慰劑相比，發現會減少軟骨厚度<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = McAlindon TE, LaValley MP, Harvey WF, Price LL, Driban JB, Zhang M, Ward RJ | title = Effect of Intra-articular Triamcinolone vs Saline on Knee Cartilage Volume and Pain in Patients With Knee Osteoarthritis: A Randomized Clinical Trial | journal = JAMA | volume = 317 | issue = 19 | pages = 1967–1975 | date = May 2017 | pmid = 28510679 | pmc = 5815012 | doi = 10.1001/jama.2017.5283 }}</ref>。2018年的研究發現關節內注射去炎松與[[眼壓|眼壓]]升高有關<ref>{{cite journal|vauthors=Taliaferro K, Crawford A, Jabara J, Lynch J, Jung E, Zvirbulis R, Banka T|title=Intraocular Pressure Increases After Intraarticular Knee Injection With Triamcinolone but Not Hyaluronic Acid|url=https://www.researchgate.net/publication/323704421|access-date=8 April 2018|format=Epub abstract ahead of print|journal=Clinical Orthopaedics and Related Research|volume=476|issue=7|pages=1420–1425|type=Level-II therapeutic study|date=9 March 2018|doi=10.1007/s11999.0000000000000261|issn=1528-1132|lccn= 53007647|oclc=01554937|pmid=29533245|pmc=6437574|via=[[ResearchGate|ResearchGate]]}}</ref>。

== 超音波導引 ==
肌肉骨骼的標準介入程序包括回顧先前的[[醫學影像|醫學影像]]檢查、病患[[知情同意|知情同意]]、適當的[[局部麻醉|局部麻醉]]。通常建議使用高頻（大於 10 MHz）線形陣列超音波探頭，有時可能需要低頻曲線陣列探頭以觀察深層結構。[[医学超声检查|超音波診斷檢查]]可能包括穿刺區域的[[彩色超音波|彩色超音波]]，對於確認鄰近神經血管結構的關係十分重要<ref name="YeapRobinson2017">Initially largely copied from: {{cite journal|last1=Yeap|first1=Phey Ming|last2=Robinson|first2=Philip|title=Ultrasound Diagnostic and Therapeutic Injections of the Hip and Groin|journal=Journal of the Belgian Society of Radiology|volume=101|issue=S2|pages=6|year=2017|issn=2514-8281|doi=10.5334/jbr-btr.1371|pmid=30498802|pmc=6251072}}<br>[https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/ Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International License (CC-BY 4.0)] {{Wayback|url=https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/ |date=20171016050101 }}</ref>。

